==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tench
<hw>Tench</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF. <ets>tenche</ets>,
F. <ets>tanche</ets>, L. <ets>tinca</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A European fresh-water fish (<spn>Tinca tinca</spn>, or <spn>Tinca
vulgaris</spn>) allied to the carp. It is noted for its tenacity of
life.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

